'''必品阁'''（{{lang-ko|비비고}}，{{lang-en|Bibigo}}）是韩国[[CJ希杰集团|CJ希杰集团]]旗下的一个国际性连锁餐饮品牌，在[[中華人民共和國|中国]]、[[美国|美国]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[英国|英国]]、[[日本|日本]]等多个国家拥有[[连锁店|连锁店]]<ref name=cjfoodville /><ref name=psy>{{cite web  |url =http://chihe.sohu.com/20130624/n379716729.shtml  |title =“PSY IN CHINA” 引爆bibigo美食狂欢夜  |publisher =搜狐网  |date =2013-06-24  |access-date =2015-05-16  |archive-date =2016-03-04  |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202556/http://chihe.sohu.com/20130624/n379716729.shtml  |dead-url =no  }}</ref>。必品阁的英文名称“Bibigo”是韩语“[[韩式拌饭|拌一拌]]”和英文“To go”（打包带走）拼合一起而成的<ref name=pinpai>{{cite web  |url=http://www.cjfoodvillechina.com/brand/brand_info.asp  |title=品牌介绍  |publisher=CJ Foodville官网  |accessdate=2015-05-16  |archive-date=2020-02-08  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208092747/http://www.cjfoodvillechina.com/brand/brand_info.asp  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。艺人[[PSY|PSY]]是必品阁的形象代言人<ref name=psy /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://finance.china.com.cn/consume/20141222/2864546.shtml |title=CJ国际韩餐品牌“必品阁”入驻北京世贸天阶 |publisher=中国网财经 |date=2014-12-22 |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518172508/http://finance.china.com.cn//consume/20141222/2864546.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

必品阁倡导“新鲜、健康”的饮食文化。其餐饮理念是以[[韩国料理|韩国传统料理]]为基础，结合世界各地顾客的口味。2014年必品阁[[伦敦苏活区|伦敦苏活区]]店成功入选世界餐饮行业历史悠久的权威鉴定机构[[米其林|米其林]]出版的《[[米其林指南|米其林指南]]》<ref>{{ko icon}}{{cite web |url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2013100708503440880 |title=英 비비고, 미슐랭 가이드 등재 |publisher=아시아경제 |date=2013-10-07 |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112606/http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2013100708503440880 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://korea.people.com.cn/206488/8449270.html |title=必品阁Bibigo入选《2014米其林指南》 |publisher=人民网 |date=2013-11-07 |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102931/http://korea.people.com.cn/206488/8449270.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

必品阁的[[韩式拌饭|拌饭]]很有特点，从米饭到酱料都可以由顾客自行选择<ref name=pinpai /><ref name=hxjw>{{cite web |url=http://www.huaxia.com/hxjk/zhms/ctsl/2015/04/4366874.html |title=必品阁bibigo：比普通韩食快一点 |publisher=华夏经纬网 |date=2015-04-21 |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924031745/http://www.huaxia.com/hxjk/zhms/ctsl/2015/04/4366874.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了拌饭外，必品阁还提供诸如[[骨董面|骨董面]]、[[韩式炸鸡|韩式炸鸡]]、什锦火锅、[[参鸡汤|参鸡汤]]、[[炒年糕|炒年糕]]、[[朝鮮蔥餅|海鲜葱饼]]等传统[[韩国料理|韩国料理]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bibigo.com/recipes/recipes|title=菜谱类别|publisher=必品阁官网|accessdate=2015-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518084803/http://www.bibigo.com/recipes/recipes|archivedate=2015-05-18|df=}}</ref><ref name=hxjw /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnfood.cn/n/2015/0421/53132.html |title=不出国门尝鲜韩国当季美味料理 |publisher=中国食品报 |date=2015-04-21 |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518095659/http://www.cnfood.cn/n/2015/0421/53132.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

